                            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-gray-800">Temporal Tag Strategy</h4>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3">Incorporate time-sensitive tags that can help resurface relevant content during specific seasons, events, or trending periods throughout the year.</p>
                            <div class="bg-green-50 p-3 rounded text-sm">
