                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Tag Stuffing and Over-Tagging</h4>
                                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Using excessive numbers of tags or irrelevant tags to try to capture more traffic. This dilutes the effectiveness of your tagging system and can negatively impact SEO.</p>
                            </div>
